Package Gui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MultiplayerGui
    This interface contains abstract methods needed in Graphical User Interface of a Multiplayer(Player+Bots) game of DominoGame.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardinalGui
    This class represents the Graphical User Interface reffering to the Cardinal Domino Type Of Game.
    GameTypeDialog
    This class represents a Menu for the player to choose which game to play(Solo1,Hungarian,Cardinal) and the number of players at it.
    HungarianGui
    This class represents the Graphical User Interface of the Hungarian type of DominoGame.
    i18n
    This class is used for internationalization reasons.
    InformationDialog
    This class represents an information Dialog that consists of a photo of this game's designers.
    Solo1Gui
    This class represents the Graphical User Interface reffering to the Solo1 Domino Type Of Game.
    StartingPage
    This class represents the Starting Page(main menu) of the games.
